Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:14.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}未完成のパズル
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:23.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}どうしてだろう? 何かが足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:28.59,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}行き違いの運命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:37.89,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}離れてゆくことも　知りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:43.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}また歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:50.07,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I Stay Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:57.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}今は一人　闇をさまようだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:15.06,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}想定外の切なさが　胸の中　消えぬままで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.70,0:22:14.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}尚未完成的拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.00,0:22:23.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}這是為何  到底還欠缺什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.38,0:22:28.59,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}擦肩而過的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.76,0:22:37.89,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}雖然知道你終將離我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:43.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我仍會繼續走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.44,0:22:50.07,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我還能堅持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:57.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}即使現在隻身一人徘徊在黑夜之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:23:15.06,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}那意想不到的悲傷至今仍刺痛我的心房  定會銘肌鏤骨
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.94,0:24:24.94,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,675)\fsp5\c&HFFFFFF&}自稱騎士  菜月{\fn微软雅黑}·{\r\c&H6D6D6D&}昴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs+3\pos(1030,404)\c&HAD6B77&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}D{\fs-3}mg{\r\c&H000000&\fn方正准圆_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}:{\r\c&H000000&}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6}國\N\N\h\h\h\h\h{\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK}        {\fn方正小标宋_GBK\fs-1}組
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1046,275)}動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\pos(1109,300)}漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\fs-1\pos(1129,393)}字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.98,0:01:27.98,Title,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord5\blur6\c&H000000&\fs-1\pos(1188,417)}幕
